high_descs: Turn around and walk forward, then turn left and walk over to the counter with the coffee machine on it.
Pick up the metal spoon off of the counter.
Walk over to the stove and look up at the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the spoon inside the mug that is in the microwave.
Take out the mug with the spoon in it and close the microwave.
Walk over to the counter to the right of the sink.
Put the mug with the spoon in it down on the front of the counter to the left of the metal pan.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a spoon in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the coffee machine on the counter.
Pick up the spoon.
Turn around and take some steps, then turn right and face the microwave above the stove.
Place the spoon inside the cup in the microwave.
Grab the cup from the microwave.
Turn right and walk then turn right again then face the counter on the left.
Place the cup on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place the cup with the spoon in it on the counter.

high_descs: Walk to the kitchen counter on your right.
Grab the spoon off the counter.
Walk to the stove to your right.
Open the microwave and place the spoon in the cup.
Grab the cup from the microwave.
Walk to the kitchen counter where the toaster is on your left.
Place the cup on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a spoon in a cup and move the cup from the microwave to the counter.
